Class GetVarBlock

  • java.lang.Object
    • ide.backend.blocks.variablesAndTypes.GetVarBlock
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Block

    public class GetVarBlock
extends java.lang.Object
implements Block
    This Block is used to use the content of a variable. The execute of the block will return the variable of the given name found in the top functionFrame or in the member of the instance of the process.
